ation payment, etc. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>To save your time and effort I have personally handpicked best WordPress donations and fundraising plugins. They are ranked in the following order: </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. GiveWP </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large theme-image\"><img src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GiveWp-Donation-Screen_Shot-1024x476.png\" alt=\"GiveWp-Donation-Screen_Shot.png\" class=\"wp-image-7532\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GiveWp-Donation-Screen_Shot-1024x476.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GiveWp-Donation-Screen_Shot-300x139.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GiveWp-Donation-Screen_Shot-768x357.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GiveWp-Donation-Screen_Shot.png 1322w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>GiveWP is one of the best WordPress Donation and Fundraising plugins having best-designed donation &amp; fundraising tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is the most downloaded donation plugin that has the highest rating from its users. For WordPress, it is the best-supported fundraising &amp; donation plugin. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, GiveWp is a powerful donation platform where it is built for all kinds of fundraising needs as well as for accepting and giving an online donation. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Furthermore, GiveWP has lots of features such as view donation statistics, manage donors, view donation reports, accepting charitable donation via customizable donation forms, and you will be able to integrate a variety of third-party gateway services. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Full-Featured Reporting</li><li>Multiple Payment Gateways</li><li>Easy Donation Payments</li><li>Complete Payment History</li><li>Customizable Donation Forms</li><li>Custom Form Fields</li><li>Powerful Donor Management</li><li>Recurring Donation Subscription</li><li>Multiple Display Style Options</li><li>Currency Switching for Donors</li><li>Credit Card Fee Recovery </li><li>Configurable Fundraising Goals</li><li>Ability to Import and Export Data</li><li>Tax-Deductible Receipts</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/give/\" target=\"_blank\">Details/Downloads GiveWP</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. PayPal Donation</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large theme-image\"><img src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Paypal-Donation-Screen_Shot-1024x453.png\" alt=\"Paypal-Donation-Screen_Shot.png\" class=\"wp-image-7533\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Paypal-Donation-Screen_Shot-1024x453.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Paypal-Donation-Screen_Shot-300x133.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Paypal-Donation-Screen_Shot-768x340.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Paypal-Donation-Screen_Shot.png 1374w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>PayPal Donation plugin is a powerful fundraising and donation plugins that helps you to collect money from your websites. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This PayPal donation is simple to use. Your customer can easily use their Credit Card or their PayPal account to make a donation for you. No matter where your customers live, they will be able to send you a donation via PayPal. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>PayPal Donation plugin is designed for WordPress and it works smoothly with almost every WordPress themes. You can also look at your donation records and if any problem arises you can also create a support request. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lastly, the PayPal Donation plugin has special buttons, each of the buttons contains their own Paypal account, image, language and currency. It is one of the best WordPress donation and fundraising plugins</p>\n\n\n\n<h3> Features </h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>View Donation Records</li><li>Donation Widget</li><li>Button Manager</li><li>Short Code Button Inserter on Post/Page</li><li>Supports 18 languages</li><li>Supports 25 Currencies (Built-in)</li><li>7 Different PayPal Donation Buttons</li><li>PayPal testing with SandBox mode</li><li>Options to make Monthly Recurring PayPal Donation</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-paypal-donation/\" target=\"_blank\">Details/Downloads PayPal Donation</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. PayPal Donations</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large theme-image\"><img src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Paypal-Donations-Screen_Shot-1024x451.png\" alt=\"Paypal-Donations-Screen_Shot.png\" class=\"wp-image-7534\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Paypal-Donations-Screen_Shot-1024x451.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Paypal-Donations-Screen_Shot-300x132.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Paypal-Donations-Screen_Shot-768x338.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Paypal-Donations-Screen_Shot.png 1344w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Paypal Donations is a donation plugin that adds a sidebar widget and shortcode of Paypal donation. It is one of the best WordPress donation and fundraising plugins for collecting donation money. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is very easy to set up. 