lso able to get paid with WooCommerce. Manually send fund from banks or locally by users can be approved with admin panel. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Finally, this plugin is easy to set up and use. It is convenient to manage and it is also user friendly. Therefore, your website can receive donations from all around the world. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3> Features </h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Start and End Date</li><li>Setting Featured Image</li><li>Frontend Campaign Submit Form</li><li>Recommended Price</li><li>Create Unlimited Rewards</li><li>Minimum and Maximum Price</li><li>Funding Goal</li><li>Campaign Update Status Tab</li><li>Show/Hide Backer Table</li><li>Frontend User Registration</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-fundraising-donation/\" target=\"_blank\">Details/Downloads WP Fundraising Donation</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Therefore it is the end of my blog post regarding the best WordPress donation and fundraising plugins. I hope you like my list and ranking of the plugins. Among those plugins, I like &#8220;GiveWp&#8221; due to its features. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thank you for reading my post.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any comments and recommendations please leave them in the comment box below.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-donation-and-fundraising-plugins/\">10+ Best WordPress Donation and Fundraising Plugins</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog\">Themebeez Blog</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss