about how to start your personal blog website that highlights your contents, matches your desired design layout with respect to your blogging niche and grabs the attention of audiences. Then I got you covered with these best free WordPress themes for personal blog. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You will be able to share your stories, thoughts &amp; ideas or you can even write articles or you can showcase your content and rich media such as audio, video, images, gallery, photos, quotes, etc.  among your audiences members with the best free WordPress themes for personal blog.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Here is the collection of the best free WordPress themes for personal blog</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here, I have personally handpicked these best free WordPress themes for personal blogs. These blog themes will cover many niche or area aspects of blogging like food, fashion, technology, lifestyle, wedding, beauty, cosmetics, cooking, travel and many more. I&#8217;m sure it does not disappoint you. Lists are as follows: </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Fascinate Blog </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large theme-image\"><img src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Fascinate-blog-screenshot-1024x768.png\" alt=\"Fascinate-blog-screenshot\" class=\"wp-image-4904\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Fascinate-blog-screenshot-1024x768.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Fascinate-blog-screenshot-300x225.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Fascinate-blog-screenshot-768x576.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Fascinate-blog-screenshot.png 1142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Fascinate is one of the best free WordPress themes for personal blog having a slick and minimal design layout. The great thing about this theme is its design. Fascinate Bog can be the ideal theme that you are looking for creating a blogging website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You will be able to create both personal as well as professional blogging websites. Creating blogging websites on different niches such as gourmet, travel, lifestyle, fashion, technology and so on will be easy with Fascinate Blog. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using this theme you can add media files like photos, audios, quotes, videos, images &amp; galleries to create rich content. Moreover, it showcases your content by highlighting them in front of audience members. Plus it has the most essential features that bloggers need such as author widget, social widget, speed optimized, SEO friendly, etc. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Fascinate Blog can be easily customizable through WordPress live customizer. This theme has quality codes with WordPress best practices.  Furthermore, it supports many popular plugins such as MailChimp, AMP, Jetpack, Contact Form 7, Yoast,<a href=\"https://themebeez.com/plugins/universal-google-adsense-ads-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\" Universal Google AdSense &amp; Ads Manager (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"rank-math-link\"> Universal Google AdSense &amp; Ads Manager</a>, etc This theme also has Pro version named as &#8220;<a aria-label=\"Fasciante Blog Pro (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/themes/fascinate-pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Fasciante Blog Pro</a>&#8220;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Slick modern Minimal Design</li><li>One-Click Demo Import</li><li>Drop Cap for Post Excerpt</li><li>Built-in Social Widgets </li><li>Built-in Post Widgets </li><li>Built-in Author Widgets </li><li>Lazy Load for Image</li><li>Optimized for Load time</li><li>Support Popular WordPress Plugins</li><li>SEO Friendly</li><li>Logo Options&#8217;</li><li>Codes with WordPress Standard</li><li>Responsive Design</li><li>Customer Support and Updates</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/themes/fascinate/\" target=\"_blank\">Details/Downloads Fascinate Blog</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>Masonry Blog </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large theme-image\"><img src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Masonry-Blog-1024x768.png\" alt=\"Masonry Blog Screen_Shot.Png\" class=\"wp-image-6948\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Masonry-Blog-1024x768.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Masonry-Blog-300x225.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Masonry-Blog-768x576.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Masonry-Blog.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p> Masonry Blog is a true masterpiece WordPress Blog theme in masonry-style layout, It is also one of the best free WordPress themes for personal blog having cool and trendy looks. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is an ideal theme for bloggers and includes most of the blogging tools such as typography options, color options, minimal style design, author widgets, social widgets, posts widgets and many more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using this theme you will be able to create almost any kinds of blogging websites such as fashion, food, lifestyle, photography, art galleries, wedding, technology, portfolio, etc.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Masonry blog is a true blog theme and contains quality codes, That&#8217;s why it has lighting fast speed and SEO friendly. You will be able to customize this theme with ease plus it is also user-friendly theme. It also supports popular plugins such as MailChimp, Mail Poet, <a href=\"https://themebeez.com/plugins/universal-google-adsense-ads-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"Universal Google AdSense &amp; Ads Manager (opens i