ee-blog.png 1213w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>GuCherry Blog is a modern design WordPress blog theme for bloggers. It is an eye-catching theme having clean, elegant and responsive layout design. It is designed to be perfectly fit for any kinds of blogging websites. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to share your thoughts &amp; ideas on various topics like lifestyle, education, entertainment, lifestyle, travel, food, fashion, etc then GuCherry is the perfect theme for you. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This theme is designed for bloggers and has multiple blogging layouts with well-designed widgets. It also has banner and slider options. There will be an adequate space in your site for advertisement while using this theme. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>GuCherry Blog is one of the best free WordPress themes for personal blog with Gutenberg compatible. This theme is optimized for speed and it is also SEO friendly. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3> Features </h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Eye-Catching Banner &amp; Slider</li><li>RTL Support</li><li>SEO friendly</li><li>Speed Optimization</li><li>Responsive Design </li><li>Live Customizer</li><li>Adequate Advertisement Space</li><li>Built-in Social Widgets</li><li>One-Click Demo Import</li><li>Built-in Related Post Excerpt Length</li><li>Widgets Areas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://everestthemes.com/themes/gucherry-blog-free-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Details/Downloads GuCherry Blog</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cream Blog </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large theme-image\"><img src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Cream-Blog-Screen_Shot-1024x927.png\" alt=\"Cream Blog Screen_Shot.png\" class=\"w